Warbixin CNN ah ayaa soo jeedisay in tirada dadka waayeelka ah ee Talyaaniga iyo awooda ay u leeyihiin inay tijaabiyaan dhammaan dadka laga helay fayraska ilaa iyo hadda ay sababi karaan dhimashada badan.
