Dadka ku jira xaalado gaar ahaan nugul sida hooyooyinka dhalay ama askarta dhaawacmay ee isbitaalada - waxaa ugu horeyn aqoonsaday muhiimada ay leedahay gacmaha lagu dhaqo caafimaadka aadanaha laba hormuud oo ka shaqeeya nadaafadda gacmaha bartamihii qarnigii 19aad: Ignaz Segmelweis oo ah dhakhtar reer Hungary ah oo ka shaqeeya Vienna, Austria iyo Florence Nightingale oo ah "aasaasaha Ingiriiska ee kalkaalisada casriga ah".
