Cudurka hargabka ee 2009 iyo cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 ee 2020 ayaa wadamo badan ku kiciyay wacyiga muhiimada ay leedahay in gacmaha lagu dhaqo saabuun si looga ilaaliyo cudurrada faafa ee noocaas ah.
