Catherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V., Brian J., Doreen D., Gregory V., Joel L., Lynette L., Ryan M., iyo Tony S.) iyo xubnaha kale ee kooxda hogaaminta (Grant I., Heather W., Jamie V., Jenine U, Liza S., Robin A. Ryan M., iyo Toby N.).
B'angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xidhan dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka ACE-ga ee la xiriira iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerka angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista Ang ((1-7) waxayna sidaas darteed tahay daawo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada wadnaha iyo dhiigga.
Nooca aadanaha ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa metaloenzyme zinc ku jira oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 waxay leedahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal colectin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa borotiinka maqaarka ee isku-dhafan ee loo yaqaan 'single-pass' oo lagu dhaqaajiyo habka loo yaqaan 'enzyme' ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Adeegga dheeriga ah ee ACE2 waxaa laga jebiyaa transmembrane kale oo la yiraahdo shades, taas oo keenta in borotiinka lagu milmi karo uu dhiiga u baxo, ugu dambeynna uu ku kala baxo kaadida.
ACE2 waxaa lagu helaa dhamaan xubnaha jirka: waxay ku xidhan tahay unugyada nooca II ee unugyada alveola ee sanbabada, unugyada enterocytes ee mindhicirka yar, unugyada endothelial ee xididdada iyo xididdada, iyo muruqyada jilicsan ee xididdada ee xubnaha badankood.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa qalfoofka maskaxda, xayawaanka, hypothalamus iyo maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inay u dhaqmaan sidii diidmo u ah ACE.
ACE waxay hormoonka angiotensin I u ogolaaneysaa inuu galo angiotensin II oo ah hormoonka wadnaha isku xidhaya.
ACE2 waxay ka jeexdaa asiidhka amino ee karboksiil-terminalka ah ee angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna ku dheelitirtaa biyo-qaadista angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
[des-Arg9]-ACE2 waxay burburin kartaa dhowr kale oo peptides oo ay ku jiraan bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareegga shaashadda ee gaadiidka amino acid ee SLC6A19 waxayna ku lug leedahay cudurka wadnaha.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sida barta ugu weyn ee lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayraska corona, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63;SARS-CoV (fiiraska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (fiiraska sababa COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta ACE2 ee unugyada dusha sare ee unugyada ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee spike S1 protein waxay saameyn ku yeelataa endocytosis, iyo wareejinta labada fayras iyo enzyme ee unugyada ku yaal unugyada.
Nidaamka gelitaanka waxaa sidoo kale u baahan in TMPRSS2 oo ah borotiinka Serine ee martida ah uu ka hortago borotiinka S, taas oo xannibaadda ay hadda baaritaan ku jirto daaweyn suurtagal ah, taas oo keentay in qaar ay soo gabagabeeyaan in yareynta heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka infekshanka.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, ururo badan oo xirfadlayaal ah iyo hay'ado sharciyeed ayaa ku talinaya in la sii wado daaweynta ACE-ga caadiga ah iyo daaweynta ARB.
Dib u eegis nidaamsan iyo falanqayn meta oo la daabacay 11 July 2012 ayaa lagu ogaaday in "isticmaalka ACE-ga ayaa sidoo kale la xiriira in ay hoos u dhigto halista sambabada 34% marka loo eego xakamaynta".
Intaa waxaa dheer, bukaanada halista ugu badan ee cudurka sambabada, gaar ahaan kuwa qaba cudurka wadnaha iyo wadnaha oo la xidhiidha, waxay u muuqdaan inay hoos u dhaceen halista marka la daweeyo ACE inhibitor.
Inkastoo saameynta ACE inhibitor ay ka yar tahay halista guud ee sambabada, isticmaalka ACE ayaa la xiriira hoos u dhigista dhimashada sambabada.
Dib u soo kabashada ACE-ga aadanaha ee 2 (rhACE2) waxaa loo tixgeliyaa inay tahay daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca daran ee sanbabada, waxaana lagu muujiyey inay hagaajineyso haemo-dinamikaha sambabada iyo nuugista oksijiinta ee doofaarka ee leh lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Dadka, nus-nolosha rhACE2 waxay qiyaastii tahay 10 saacadood, waxayna qaadataa 30 daqiiqo in ay bilowdo, waxayna qaadataa 24 saacadood.
Natiijada badankeedu waxay muujinaysaa in rhACE2 ay noqon karto daawo rajo leh dadka aan u dulqaadan karin daawooyinka caadiga ah ee loo yaqaan 'Renin-angiotensin system inhibitors' (RAS inhibitors) ama cudurada leh heerarka sare ee 'angiotensin imbalance'.
