Dowladda ayaa sheegtay 12 April 2020 in barnaamijku uu ku jiro marxalado horumarineed oo uu heli doono toddobaadyo gudahood. Barnaamij la mid ah ayaa lagu qorsheeyay Ireland iyo Faransiiska ("Stop COVID").
Australia iyo New Zealand ayaa labada dal ka fekeraya barnaamijyo ku saleysan Singapore ee Trace Together iyo Blue Tooth Protocol. Ruushka ayaa damacsan inuu soo bandhigo barnaamijyo loo yaqaan 'geofencing apps' oo loogu talagalay bukaannada COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow, si loo hubiyo inaysan ka bixin guryahooda.
Ross Anderson oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay injineernimada amniga ee jaamacadda Cambridge ayaa ku taxay dhibaatooyin badan oo macquul ah oo ku saabsan nidaamyada ku saleysan AAP, oo ay ku jiraan xaqiijinta xaqiiqooyinka been abuurka ah iyo suurtagalnimada waxtarka yar ee AAP haddii ay isticmaasho dad aad u yar.
Iyada oo walaac ka muujineysa faafitaanka barnaamijyada khalkhal gelinaya ama waxyeelada leh ee "Covid-19", Apple waxay xaddiday noocyada ururada ay ku dari karaan barnaamijyada la xiriira cudurka coronavirus dukaankooda, iyadoo ku xaddidaya kaliya "rukhsadaha" ama hay'adaha kale ee sumcad leh.
