Xogta hore waxay muujineysaa in qiyaasta sare ee loo yaqaan 'rybavirin' ay lagama maarmaan tahay si loo xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 ee tijaabada.
Nidazoxanide waxaa lagu taliyey in la tijaabiyo ka dib markii la muujiyey in ay ka hortagto heerarka hoose ee SARS-CoV-2. Daraasadaha ayaa muujiyay in horudhaca borotiinka 'spike protein priming' ee loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protease serine 2' (TMPRSS2) uu aad ugu baahan yahay in SARS-CoV-2 ay u gudubto iyada oo la falgasho ACE-2 farsamo-yaqaanka.
Daraasadaha loo sameeyay chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo ay la socdaan ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leeyihiin dhibaatooyin waaweyn oo ka hortagay bulshada caafimaadka inay u wareegaan daaweyntaas illaa daraasad dheeraad ah. Ocelta-mivir ma joojin SARS-CoV-2 tijaabooyinka, mana jirto wax door ah oo la ogyahay oo lagu ogaaday daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa mid aad u adag marxaladaha dambe ee COVID-19.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaysa in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay sifooyin ka hortag ah duufaanta cytokine. Tosalizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha kadib daraasad yar.
Talyaaniga ayaa ku socda tijaabooyin heer qaran ah oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo wajiga 2 ah, kadib markii ay muujiyeen natiijooyin wanaagsan oo ku saabsan dadka qaba cudurrada daran.
Marka la isku daro baaritaanka dhiigga ee serum ferritin si loo ogaado duufaanta cytokine, waxay ka dhigan tahay in la hortago horumarka, taas oo loo maleynayo inay sababtay dhimashada dadka qaar ee qaba cudurka.
Sanadkii 2017, FDA ayaa ansixisay interleukin-6 neurotransmitter antagonist iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasad hore oo lagu sameeyay daaweynta cudurka loo yaqaan 'CAR T cell therapy', oo ah cudurka loo yaqaan 'steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome' oo ah cudur la isku halleyn karo.
Ilaa iyo hadda ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo muujinaya in tosalizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
Waxaa la baaray in la sameeyo hab aan tallaal ahayn oo lagu wareejiyo unugyada la nadiifiyey iyo kuwa la isku halleyn karo ee ay soo saaraan nidaamka difaaca ee dadka ka bogsaday COVID-19 si loo gaarsiiyo dadka u baahan.
istaraatijiyaddan waxaa loo isticmaalay SARS, laakiin wax saameyn ah kama helin.
Xadgudubka fayraska waa habka la filayo ee loo adeegsado daaweynta antibody-ka aan la isticmaalin ee SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, farsamooyin kale, sida antibody-ku tiirsan cytotoxicity-ka unugyada iyo/ama phagocytes-ka, ayaa suurtagal ah.
Noocyada kale ee daaweynta antibody-ka ee aan shaqeyn ayaa la horumarinayaa, tusaale ahaan, isticmaalka monoclonal antibodies-ka la sameeyay.
Wax soo saarka serum-ka qallalan, oo ay ku jiraan borotiinka dhiigga ee bukaannada la bogsiiyay oo ay ku jiraan unugyada difaaca ee gaarka ah ee fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo kordhiyo koritaanka.
Cudurka Coronavirus, waa koox ka mid ah cudurrada la xiriira
Li Wenliang, oo ah dhakhtar ka tirsan Isbitaalka Dhexe ee Wuhan, ayaa ku dhacay COVID-19 kadib markii uu kor u qaaday wacyiga faafitaanka fayraska, wuxuuna dhintay.
